{"note":"Now improve the generated app by doing the following:\n\n1. Make the daily timeline visually excellent on mobile.\n2. Add a case-matching confidence indicator to each suggested entry.\n3. Add edit modal for suggested entries with:\n   - case selector\n   - description editor\n   - duration editor in tenths\n   - billable toggle\n4. Add merge selected suggestions action.\n5. Add split suggestion action.\n6. Add a dashboard summary showing:\n   - suggested hours today\n   - approved hours today\n   - number of unreviewed suggestions\n7. Add realistic seeded demo data for a plaintiff-side employment lawyer.\n8. Improve all styling to feel polished and startup-quality.\n9. Ensure all pages compile cleanly with no TypeScript errors.\n10. Update the README with exact run instructions.","textColorIndex":0,"bgColorIndex":0}